int g1/0/9
desc To compute node 3 - Storage VLAN
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 402
no shut


! CONTROLLER

int g1/0/10
desc To controller - Management VLAN
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 400
no shut


! STORAGE

int g1/0/11
desc To ISCSI - Management VLAN
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 400
no shut

int g1/0/12
desc To ISCSI - Storage VLAN
switchport mode access
switchport access vlan 402
no shut


